@node Introduction
@toc main
 
 First of all, please apologize my English ! I am French and it took a lot of time writing this english documentation.

 You are now seeing the newest version of SmallPlayer, a small module player. It can now decode XPKed modules, but it is still small, about 50 kb, so it will be a good tool for low-memory amiga. I hope you'll enjoy Sp, Sincerely

 @{"Mathieu Chčnebit" LINK Auteur}

@endnode

