@node SmallPlayer
@toc main

 A baby could use SmallPlayer so it is simple ! Choose a module by clicking on the uppper arrow, play it with the triangle gadget, jump the module positon with left and right arrows, pause the module with || button.

 You can acces the same options with the menus that appeared with smallPlayer version 1.5

 I think that's all you need to know to make good use of SmallPlayer
 
@endnode
@node Historique "Historic"
@toc main

@{u}Historic@{uu}:

@{bg fill}   @{bg background}  Version 1.5 :

	_ Total XPacked module support. 

	_ Volume Scroller is redefined in real time.

	_ New menus to acces the same options that with the buttons.

	_ Buttons Shapes are included in Binary mode, so it's easier to move SmallPlayer from a directory.

	_ Some small bugs were deleted.

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} Version 1.0 :

	_ First redistributed version, directly inspired from the articles I made in the French magazine Amiga News.
@endnode
@endnode
